metadata.name: Bloom at your own time
metadata.description:
"Take a second, the wait may seem long but patience will always be rewarded, feel everything around you, fill your lungs with that air and nourish yourself with that water, let it flow and you will see how you will return to the world flourished and ready for adventures that are yet to come".

It represents calm, waiting, patience, the moment in which we nourish ourselves with everything that surrounds us just before blooming and going out into the outside world.

Chelsy Escalona
